    "允许：满足条件可访问；拒绝：满足即禁止；绕过：对满足条件的流量跳过 Access 校验。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "السماح: من يطابق يمكنه الوصول؛ الرفض: من يطابق يُحظر؛ التجاوز: تخطّي فحص Access للحركة المطابقة."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Zulassen: passende Nutzer erhalten Zugriff; Verweigern: passende Nutzer werden blockiert; Umgehen: Access-Prüfung für passenden Traffic überspringen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Allow: matching users can access; Deny: matching users are blocked; Bypass: skip Access checks for matching traffic."
          }
        },
        "es-MX" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Permitir: los que cumplen acceden; Denegar: los que cumplen quedan bloqueados; Omitir: salta la verificación de Access para el tráfico que cumple."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Autoriser : les utilisateurs correspondants accèdent ; Refuser : ils sont bloqués ; Contourner : ignore la vérification Access pour le trafic correspondant."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "許可：条件に合うユーザーはアクセス可。拒否：条件に合うとブロック。バイパス：条件に合うトラフィックは Access 検証をスキップ。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "허용: 조건 충족 시 접근 가능. 거부: 충족 시 차단. 우회: 충족하는 트래픽은 Access 검사를 건너뜁니다."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Permitir: quem corresponde acessa; Negar: quem corresponde é bloqueado; Ignorar: pula a verificação do Access para o tráfego correspondente."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Permitir: quem corresponde acede; Recusar: quem corresponde é bloqueado; Ignorar: salta a verificação do Access para o tráfego correspondente."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "İzin ver: eşleşen kullanıcılar erişebilir; Reddet: eşleşenler engellenir; Atla: eşleşen trafik için Access denetimini atla."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "允許：符合條件者可存取；拒絕：符合即封鎖；略過：對符合條件的流量略過 Access 驗證。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "允許：符合條件者可存取；拒絕：符合即封鎖；略過：對符合條件的流量略過 Access 驗證。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
